{"tid":2111134,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【中印衝突】印媒：解放軍準備討論撤離班公錯湖　有望破僵局","createTime":"2020-07-16T10:37:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-16T11:06:25.000Z","uid":69574,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"1e4e4c93af912db95b5bfa7c2d5447e195c0da0d","tid":2111134,"uid":69574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T10:37:01.000Z","msg":"《印度快報》7月16日發表題為《（印度）官員說，LAC（實際控制線）會談非常積極，解放軍準備討論班公錯湖》的報道，稱會談取得積極迹象，雙方有望「打破僵局」。<br />\n<br />\n報道稱，在班公錯湖，中國軍隊已經到達第8指（ Finger 8）以西8公里處，印度稱這是實控線。雖然解放軍已經撤離了第4指（Finger 4）基地，但解放軍仍在佔領那裏的山脊地帶。<br />\n<br />\n中印高級軍事指揮官於7月14日在拉達克（Ladakh）東部的久舒爾（Chushul）舉行了第四輪軍長級談判，會談持續了將近15個小時。<br />\n<br />\n印度第14軍團司令辛格（Harinder Singh）中將與中國南疆軍區司令柳林少將出席了第四輪軍長級會談。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/498593/%E4%B8%AD%E5%8D%B0%E8%A1%9D%E7%AA%81-%E5%8D%B0%E5%AA%92-%E8%A7%A3%E6%94%BE%E8%BB%8D%E6%BA%96%E5%82%99%E8%A8%8E%E8%AB%96%E6%92%A4%E9%9B%A2%E7%8F%AD%E5%85%AC%E9%8C%AF%E6%B9%96-%E6%9C%89%E6%9C%9B%E7%A0%B4%E5%83%B5%E5%B1%80\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%2F498593%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%258D%25B0%25E8%25A1%259D%25E7%25AA%2581-%25E5%258D%25B0%25E5%25AA%2592-%25E8%25A7%25A3%25E6%2594%25BE%25E8%25BB%258D%25E6%25BA%2596%25E5%2582%2599%25E8%25A8%258E%25E8%25AB%2596%25E6%2592%25A4%25E9%259B%25A2%25E7%258F%25AD%25E5%2585%25AC%25E9%258C%25AF%25E6%25B9%2596-%25E6%259C%2589%25E6%259C%259B%25E7%25A0%25B4%25E5%2583%25B5%25E5%25B1%2580&d=q%2BUwj3SihaKoadPXZHTFaXljxErbpFF6VcGzQu2DuOQ%3D&h=477bbbea\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/498593/%E4%B8%AD%E5%8D%B0%E8%A1%9D%E7%AA%81-%E5%8D%B0%E5%AA%92-%E8%A7%A3%E6%94%BE%E8%BB%8D%E6%BA%96%E5%82%99%E8%A8%8E%E8%AB%96%E6%92%A4%E9%9B%A2%E7%8F%AD%E5%85%AC%E9%8C%AF%E6%B9%96-%E6%9C%89%E6%9C%9B%E7%A0%B4%E5%83%B5%E5%B1%80</a>"},{"pid":"97828fa183828298d64742871cc9eedd4355d48f","tid":2111134,"uid":25900,"like":10,"dis